description: Deletes a custom permissions profile from a user.

parameters.name: UserName
parameters.description: The username of the user that you want to remove custom permissions from.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the custom permission configuration that you want to delete.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The namespace that the user belongs to.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
